Yae9Y_1eV8f6fmtOkn3lfelzgXtcn9dI9k0-klu8P1md9jeQLM0tb7X4PGYINh5A3e6xTOf9_N4=
JDABfssGiJDP5SsCJS6DvHDS1FxsSYV_oT8bCnsb] and then ask for a raise.
If you=E2=80=99re an investor with SaaS or digital subscription businesses =
in your portfolio, tell them to sign up for Pipe to avoid unnecessary dilut=
ion in future rounds and keep your pro rata allocation to make more investm=
ents, and then tell those founders to sign up for Pipe [https://email.mg2.s=
ubstack.com/c/eJxFUMtuwyAQ_BpztHg6-MChUpXfsLDZOjQ2EFja-O9L4kOllVa7o9nZmcUir=
